s in equipment in a future version of MAKRO.
\end_layout

\end_inset

.
 The majority of public production is accounted for as government consumption
 of public goods and services, 
\begin_inset Formula $G_{t}^{\text{Pub}}$
\end_inset

, however.
\end_layout

